title: A Castle On Top of A Hill: The True Story of Fanny
itunes:title: A Castle On Top of A Hill: The True Story of Fanny
description: The rock band Fanny ruled the Sunset Strip in the 1970s, and they were supposed to be the next big thing. They explain the price women pay for being ahead of their time.
